{"Id":486,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-mazhonggang","Author":"Ma Zhong Gang","Language":"Chinese(simplified)","Description":"Chinese(simplified)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"https://alquran.cloud/api","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":93,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"以上午 [太阳升起后]发誓，"},{"SurahNumber":93,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"以寂静时的黑夜发誓，"},{"SurahNumber":93,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"你[穆圣]的主既没有丢弃你，也没有怨恨你[注]。"},{"SurahNumber":93,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"后世对你的确比今世好。"},{"SurahNumber":93,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"你的主必将赏赐你，你将因此而喜悦。"},{"SurahNumber":93,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"难道他[安拉]没有发现你[穆圣]是孤儿而赐给你庇护吗？"},{"SurahNumber":93,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"难道他没有发现你徘徊歧途而引导你吗？"},{"SurahNumber":93,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"难道他没有发现你贫穷而使你富裕吗？"},{"SurahNumber":93,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"因此，你不要虐待孤儿，"},{"SurahNumber":93,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"你不要斥退乞求者，"},{"SurahNumber":93,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"你当宣扬你的主的恩惠。"}]}